title.value: "A Sketch of the Life of John A. Steinbeck, the Dickson Family and the Jewish Mission in Palestine Asia," approximately 30pp, [233] c. 1917

note.value: Composition notebook of the history of the John A. Steinbeck and Almira Steinbeck and their families - the Steinbecks and the Dicksons. Includes descriptions of their lives in Germany, Palestine and the United States during the American Civil War.
